1 (III) PROVIDE FOR ADVERTISING AND PROMOTION OF
2 COLLECTION OPPORTUNITIES THROUGHOUT THE STATE AND ON A REGULAR BASIS,
3 AS DESCRIBED IN § 9–1728.2 OF THIS SUBTITLE;
