5 THROUGHOUT THE STATE, THAT INCLUDES, AT A MINIMUM, CONVENIENT SERVICE
6 THROUGH A NETWORK OF COLLECTION SITES DISTRIBUTED TO ENSURE THAT 95%
7 OF THE RESIDENTS OF THE STATE ARE WITHIN 15 MILES OF A COLLECTION SITE
8 AVAILABLE FOR THEIR USE AS FOLLOWS:
9 1. IN EACH COUNTY THAT HAS A POPULATION OF LESS
10 THAN 100,000 RESIDENTS, AT LEAST ONE COLLECTION SITE;
